♪Replacing the weight of tears
with that of sweat♪

00:42:55.576 --> 00:43:00.897
♪Covering the gunshot's sound
with wounds♪

00:43:02.970 --> 00:43:07.824
♪No one is born unyielding and strong♪

00:43:08.630 --> 00:43:11.777
♪But because someone
always rushes ahead♪

00:43:11.777 --> 00:43:14.881
♪To shield us from the storm♪

00:43:17.537 --> 00:43:22.671
♪When every extraordinary act
